{
  "name": "enhance-the-video-editor-20260406-0259",
  "idea": "Enhance the video editor right-click context menu to show existing shots associated with selected clips. Current behavior: After creating a shot from selected clips, clearSelection() runs and Create Shot/Generate Video buttons disappear on subsequent right-clicks. The menu has no awareness of existing shots. Desired: 1) When right-clicking clips, check if existing shots contain those generation IDs. 2) At TOP of shot actions section, list each existing shot by name with inline Jump to Shot and Generate Video buttons. 3) Below existing shots, still show Create Shot and Generate Video buttons. 4) Fix the clearSelection() bug. 5) Works for single and multi-clip selections. 6) Works in both ClipAction context menu and SelectionContextMenu.",
